In realtime enterprise applications, Helm is mainly used to standardize, automate, version, and manage Kubernetes deployments across environments.

Why Companies Use Helm

Without Helm:

huge YAML files
duplicate configs
manual updates
difficult rollback
environment mismatch

With Helm:

reusable templates
parameterized configs
versioned deployments
easy upgrades/rollback
environment-specific values
Realtime Enterprise Flow
1. Developer Creates Application

