Very widely used by SRE teams.

Realtime Production Issues You’ll See
Common Problems
Problem	Root Cause
OutOfSync	manual kubectl changes
ImagePullBackOff	wrong image tag
Degraded	pods failing
Sync Failed	bad Helm template
CrashLoopBackOff	app issue
Important Enterprise Concepts
Helm Is NOT Deployment Automation

Helm only:

templates manifests
packages apps

ArgoCD:

continuously deploys
reconciles state

This distinction is extremely important.

